<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> vikra</hi>ma coḻa<hi rend="grantha">de</hi>vaṟku yāṇṭu muṉṟāvataṟketirāvatu Akaḷaṅka nāṭāḻ
<lb n="2" break="no"/><unclear>v</unclear>āṉ Olai tiṅkaḷurum Ūrāḷikaḷuṅ kaṇṭu taṅkaḷūr nāyaṉār ca<hi rend="grantha">ndra</hi>puri<hi rend="grantha">śvara</hi>m Uṭaiya
<lb n="3" break="no"/>nāyaṉārukkup paṅkuṉit tirunāḷpaṭikku Ivvūril Iṟaiyeṇṇaināṟpattaiññ<unclear>ā</unclear> 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ḻiyum Aiñcuṭṭi yeṇṇai Eḻukuṟuṇi nāṉāḻiyum Āka Eṇṇaikalaṉe kuṟuṇi Oru
<lb n="5"/>nāḻiyum Ivvūril Iṟaik<unclear>ā</unclear>ṇiyil muppatiṉ kalakāṇiyu c<unclear>e</unclear>lliṭṭukkoṇṭu tiruṉāḷ
<lb n="6"/>Oru kuṟaivaṟa ca<hi rend="grantha">ndrādi</hi>ttavarai Eḻuntaruḷivippate Ippaṭikku Akaḷaṅkaṉāṭāḻvā<unclear>ṉ</unclear>
<lb n="7"/>Eḻuttu Ivai vicai<unclear>yakāmav</unclear>eḷāṉ Eḻuttu Itu pa<hi rend="grantha">nmāheśvararakṣai <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied></hi>
</p>

